com.appdynamics.instrumentation.sdk

Class Rule

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.appdynamics.instrumentation.sdk.Rule

  • public class Rule
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides a builder pattern to allow creation of Rules for consumption by Instrumentation SDK template classes. This is intended for use by the initializeRules method of the various templates. Created by ryan.terbush on 3/22/16.
